Class albumViewController

  • java.lang.Object
    • controller.albumViewController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, javafx.fxml.Initializable

    public class albumViewController
extends java.lang.Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable, java.io.Serializable
    Displays all albums created by users. Allows the creation of new albums and the deletion of albums. Stores the data entered by serializing the path names into their respective user folders.
    Author:
    Rizwan Khan(mrk150) && Ahmed Ghoneim(asg179)
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
